        <updateDate>2007-05-23T19:13:56Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Leasehold Improvement Depreciation Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) make permanent the accelerated depreciation of qualified leasehold improvement property (i.e., a 15-year recovery period); and (2) modify the rule for determining the adjustment to earnings and profits for depreciation of such property.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
